text: The Most Beautiful Couple () is a 2018 German drama film directed by Sven Taddicken. It was screened in the Contemporary World Cinema section at the 2018 Toronto International Film Festival. ==Cast== * Maximilian Brückner as Malte * Luise Heyer as Liv * Florian Bartholomäi as Henning * Jasna Fritzi Bauer as Jenny * Inga Birkenfeld as Maren ==References== ==External links== * Category:2018 films Category:2018 drama films Category:German films Category:German drama films Category:German-language films
